Package: netmeta
Title: Network Meta-Analysis using Frequentist Methods
Version: 6.6-6
Date: 2019-12-20
Depends: meta (>= 4.9-8)
Imports: magic, MASS, ggplot2 (>= 3.0.0)
Suggests: colorspace, rgl, hasseDiagram (>= 0.1.3), grid
Authors@R: c(person("Gerta", "Rücker",
